==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: biomedicine
<hw>bi"o*med`i*cine</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The application
of the principles and techniques of the natural sciences, especially
biology, to investigate and solve problems in clinical
medicine.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The investigation of the effects of external
environmental factors such as weightlessness on the human
body.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bion</ent>⟦br⟧
